org.gearvrf

Class GVRHybridObject.CleanupHandlerListManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gearvrf.GVRHybridObject.CleanupHandlerListManager
  • Enclosing class:
    GVRHybridObject

    protected static class GVRHybridObject.CleanupHandlerListManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Small class to help descendants keep the number of lists of native cleanup handlers to a minimum. Maintains a prefix list (the static list that the descendant class passes to GVRHybridObject.GVRHybridObject(GVRContext, long, List)) and a Map of suffixes: the Map lets there be one list per descendant class that adds a list of cleanup handler(s), instead of (potentially) one list per instance. See the usage in GVRCollider.
